	(1036,'da97ead9fad8b0e375630951ebdc0948','a:2:{s:7:\"timeout\";i:1510263093;s:5:\"value\";s:4477:\"{\"new_version\":\"1.0.1\",\"stable_version\":\"1.0.1\",\"name\":\"ACF Integration\",\"slug\":\"lc-acfintegration\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/livecomposerplugin.com\\/?post_type=download&#038;p=298908&#038;changelog=1\",\"last_updated\":\"2017-04-10 09:15:13\",\"homepage\":\"https:\\/\\/livecomposerplugin.com\\/?post_type=download&p=298908\",\"sections\":{\"description\":\"<p>Output with Live Composer any content from the\\u00a0custom fields. Use it on pages, posts or templates created with Live Composer page builder.<\\/p>\\n\\n<ul>\\n<li>Open <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/livecomposer.help\\/article\\/212-acf-integration\\\">Extension Documentation<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li>Get Help: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/livecomposerplugin.com\\/support\\/support-request\\/\\\">Submit Support Request<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li>Download <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/advancedcustomfields.com\\\">Advanced Custom Fields Plugin<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li>Download <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/livecomposerplugin.com\\/downloads\\/live-composer-page-builder\\/\\\">Live Composer Plugin<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\\n<h4>Drag And Drop Custom Fields<\\/h4>\\n\\n<ul>\\n<li>Drag and drop any custom field content right in the page builder.<\\/li>\\n<li>Use custom fields on a single page or site-wide templates.<\\/li>\\n<li>Speed-up the site editing process for your clients.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\\n<h4>ACF + Page Builder<\\/h4>\\n\\n<p>This extension integrates powerful and professional ACF plugin with Live Composer. It adds a group of new modules. Use these modules to output the custom fields content in any section of the page or template you are editing.<\\/p>\\n\\n<h4>Supported ACF field types<\\/h4>\\n\\n<p>After the extension installed you will find new ACF section in the Live Composer modules list with the next field types supported:<\\/p>\\n\\n<ul>\\n<li>Text<\\/li>\\n<li>Textarea<\\/li>\\n<li>Wysiwyg<\\/li>\\n<li>Number<\\/li>\\n<li>Page Link<\\/li>\\n<li>Date Picker<\\/li>\\n<li>Image<\\/li>\\n<li>Checkbox<\\/li>\\n<li>Select<\\/li>\\n<li>File<\\/li>\\n<li>Taxonomy<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\\n<p>The extension supports field suffix and prefix functionality from ACF plugin.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>To use this extension you need to have <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.advancedcustomfields.com\\\">Advanced Custom Fields ACF<\\/a> and <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/livecomposerplugin.com\\/downloads\\/live-composer-page-builder\\/\\\">Live Composer<\\/a> plugins installed.<\\/p>\",\"changelog\":\"<h4>1.0 - April 11th 2017<\\/h4>\\n\\n<ul>\\n<li>Initial release<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\"},\"banners\":{\"high\":\"\",\"low\":\"\"},\"tested\":\"4.7.3\",\"tested_up_to\":\"4.7.3\",\"stable_tag\":\"1.0\",\"description\":[\"<p>Output with Live Composer any content from the\\u00a0custom fields. Use it on pages, posts or templates created with Live Composer page builder.<\\/p>\\n\\n<ul>\\n<li>Open <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/livecomposer.help\\/article\\/212-acf-integration\\\">Extension Documentation<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li>Get Help: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/livecomposerplugin.com\\/support\\/support-request\\/\\\">Submit Support Request<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li>Download <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/advancedcustomfields.com\\\">Advanced Custom Fields Plugin<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<li>Download <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/livecomposerplugin.com\\/downloads\\/live-composer-page-builder\\/\\\">Live Composer Plugin<\\/a><\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\\n<h4>Drag And Drop Custom Fields<\\/h4>\\n\\n<ul>\\n<li>Drag and drop any custom field content right in the page builder.<\\/li>\\n<li>Use custom fields on a single page or site-wide templates.<\\/li>\\n<li>Speed-up the site editing process for your clients.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\\n<h4>ACF + Page Builder<\\/h4>\\n\\n<p>This extension integrates powerful and professional ACF plugin with Live Composer. It adds a group of new modules. Use these modules to output the custom fields content in any section of the page or template you are editing.<\\/p>\\n\\n<h4>Supported ACF field types<\\/h4>\\n\\n<p>After the extension installed you will find new ACF section in the Live Composer modules list with the next field types supported:<\\/p>\\n\\n<ul>\\n<li>Text<\\/li>\\n<li>Textarea<\\/li>\\n<li>Wysiwyg<\\/li>\\n<li>Number<\\/li>\\n<li>Page Link<\\/li>\\n<li>Date Picker<\\/li>\\n<li>Image<\\/li>\\n<li>Checkbox<\\/li>\\n<li>Select<\\/li>\\n<li>File<\\/li>\\n<li>Taxonomy<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\\n<p>The extension supports field suffix and prefix functionality from ACF plugin.<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>To use this extension you need to have <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.advancedcustomfields.com\\\">Advanced Custom Fields ACF<\\/a> and <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/livecomposerplugin.com\\/downloads\\/live-composer-page-builder\\/\\\">Live Composer<\\/a> plugins installed.<\\/p>\"],\"changelog\":[\"<h4>1.0 - April 11th 2017<\\/h4>\\n\\n<ul>\\n<li>Initial release<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\"]}\";}','yes'),
